Description: Custom pair of Oakley Penny. Shinny Copper beautiful pair. These stand out quite a bit and draw more attention than I really want at my age. The frames are very tight and have not been worn since I had them customized 5 years ago. I would say the frames are almost perfect. 9.7 / 10 The lenses are older ice blue. I would put them at 7 / 10. I have included pictures to show the lenses. The small scratches do not affect vision at all... I thought about putting some new blue prizim lenses in them, which would look amazing. These glasses are on Pinterest with a pair of copper Juliet’s I had as well. To my knowledge it is the most liked picture of any Oakley product off all time on Pinterest. They are flashy and I won’t ever wear them... They deserve to be seen in the sunlight... I want to be clear, some may feel I am asking too much for these, I really don’t want to let them go, I love these things... but my wife won’t let me pay cash out of savings for something ridiculous I’ve been eying for years, so I need to liquidate some of my collection that I will never wear. I can send more pictures if you need them here is the Pinterest. https://pin.it/jndxvhoc7tgxse
